If you intend to use syslog-ng together with the systemd journal,
please be sure to configure it to listen accordingly, e.g. replace

    unix-dgram("/dev/log");

with

    unix-dgram("/run/systemd/journal/syslog");

in /etc/syslog-ng/syslog-ng.conf
